Language: en

00:00:00.500 --> 00:00:03.350
 Let's make a salad with veal and crackers 

00:00:03.350 --> 00:00:10.390
 Veal put in boiling salted water, bring 

00:00:10.390 --> 00:00:16.000
 boil, remove the formed foam, add bay 

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:21.619
 leaf, pepper and allspice peas and boil until tender. 

00:00:21.619 --> 00:00:24.269
 Boil carrots until tender. 

00:00:24.269 --> 00:00:27.580
 Eggs boil hard boiled. 

00:00:27.580 --> 00:00:35.210
 Onion cut into cubes, pour boiling water and leave 

00:00:35.210 --> 00:00:41.030
 for 20 minutes, then drain the water and pour the onion with the marinade. 

00:00:41.030 --> 00:00:46.059
 For the marinade: take 100 ml of boiling water, add 

00:00:46.059 --> 00:00:57.199
 2 tbsp. spoons of sugar and 2 tbsp. spoons of apple cider vinegar. 

00:00:57.199 --> 00:01:07.610
 Chilled veal cut into cubes, 

00:01:07.610 --> 00:01:14.140
 Put the first layer of lettuce, cover with mayonnaise. 

00:01:14.140 --> 00:01:17.990
 Put the pickled onions. 

00:01:17.990 --> 00:01:22.230
 Grate carrots on a coarse grater, put on top 

00:01:22.230 --> 00:01:26.010
 onions, cover with a grid of mayonnaise. 

00:01:26.010 --> 00:01:32.530
 Grate eggs, lay the next 

00:01:32.530 --> 00:01:34.250
 a layer of lettuce. 

00:01:34.250 --> 00:01:40.400
 Sliced ​​loaf, cut into small cubes, lay out 

00:01:40.400 --> 00:01:47.220
 heated pan with vegetable oil, fry 

00:01:47.220 --> 00:01:49.930
 until golden brown. 

00:01:49.930 --> 00:01:55.770
 Put the croutons in a salad bowl. 

00:01:55.770 --> 00:01:58.159
 Cover the croutons with mayonnaise just before 

00:01:58.159 --> 00:02:10.539
 Serving to the table, otherwise the croutons will soften and will not be crispy. 

00:02:10.539 --> 00:02:11.539
 Enjoy your meal! 

